speech: Three statisticians went out hunting, and came across a large deer. The first statistician fired, but missed, by a meter to the left. The second statistician fired, but also missed, by a meter to the right. The third statistician didn’t fire, but shouted in triumph, “On the average we got it!”
why do we tell actors to "break a leg"?  because every  play has a cast!!
I once fell in love with an encyclopedia... I was completely in-fact-uated
